Jean Carson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Carson 0 Jean Carson (February 28, 1923 – November 2, 2005) was an American stage, film and television actress best known for her work on the classic 1960s sitcom The Andy Griffith Show as one of the "fun girls".
